{"tid":1325332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Mon Post警犬請入] 以為無委任證就無事根本係on9","createTime":"2019-07-17T00:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T18:37:07.000Z","uid":61886,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b32c9d5cd4a8d38738b948bcf56f4253298009e9","tid":1325332,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:12:54.000Z","msg":"個大意係節錄返劉細良既其中一集節目：<br />\n<br />\n七警案有影到委任證咩<br />\n有影到樣咩<br />\n剩係影到咁架咋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4C7C7cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4C7C7cc.png&h=04a0a911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後結果係點？<br />\n咪7個一齊坐<br />\n<br />\n而家林奠撐無條件撐你地<br />\n佢想再升級個警民衝突矛盾<br />\n一係是但一邊有人死<br />\n然後？<br />\n林奠就會下台<br />\n下一任特首上台<br />\n所有罪名歸落林奠到<br />\n而警犬必定會被清算<br />\n用黎換取新特首既管治威信同蜜月期<br />\n因為警犬喺中共眼中<br />\n只係condom<br />\n<br />\n警犬愈打 我地愈要出<br />\n警犬愈暴力 只會愈多人以武制暴<br />\n最後 警犬入醫院 入浩園 定入監倉<br />\n都係自己拎黎<br />\n<br />\n721 Full Gear 金鐘見"},{"pid":"23377290b0d8f5168a070a778094b93f121d9187","tid":1325332,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb80dedc6f8ce796614aa9f7f7fe2f298f54cb5f","tid":1325332,"uid":61886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:16:27.000Z","msg":"成班警犬以為遮樣無委任證就可以開無雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都唔緊要<br />\n你地入左去坐<br />\n你地啲手足會幫手照顧你地老婆架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2a3919645f910a70d726165a1610a42bb1e388","tid":1325332,"uid":61886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23377290b0d8f5168a070a778094b93f121d9187","tid":1325332,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:16:50.000Z","msg":"黑人問號？"},{"pid":"658ad29d425b1e2ad5cc9179553d648c2593126d","tid":1325332,"u